05:31.120 --> 05:34.200
the other problem with treating the phenomenology of spirit

05:34.200 --> 05:37.120
as like the textbook for an undergraduate Hegel course,

05:37.120 --> 05:42.240
is I'll talk about this more later today and more next week.

