01:19:44.160 --> 01:19:47.040
Or the standard has to be external

01:19:47.040 --> 01:19:48.140
to their conception of knowledge.

01:19:48.140 --> 01:19:49.640
But then it's question-making.

01:19:51.680 --> 01:19:53.520
So, what Hegel is doing

01:19:53.960 --> 01:19:56.640
